thread.title_full: Ace Rental Cars Australia & New Zealand reviewed by John

author: John
title: John
text: Pick up and drop back service from ferry was a little slow but also was one of the deciding factors in choosing ACE. We had one of the older cars no problems, clean and went well. Would us again in Auckland and will look at for car rental in Australia later this year.
